Ray Austin (director) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ray_Austin_(director) 0 Ray Austin (born 5 December 1932) is an English television and film director, television writer, novelist and former stunt performer and actor who has worked in both the United Kingdom and the United States. He served as director on episodes of some 50 programmes between 1968 and 1998.
